automatically every 20 seconds,

02:40.593 --> 02:42.593
the pigeon wonders,

02:42.883 --> 02:45.603
'What did I do to deserve this?'

02:46.974 --> 02:49.288
If it was flapping its wings at the time,

02:49.388 --> 02:52.617
