1:49:14.944 --> 1:49:16.944
Hi, Dad.

1:49:18.223 --> 1:49:19.983
Hi.

1:49:20.083 --> 1:49:22.083
Hey.

1:49:22.837 --> 1:49:25.047
I'll be in a minute, guys.

