1:51:32.986 --> 1:51:36.046
Why are you looking at me like that?

1:51:37.258 --> 1:51:39.258
Nemo.

1:51:40.015 --> 1:51:42.395
Do I take sugar in my cofee?

1:51:44.820 --> 1:51:47.245
