1:59:01.611 --> 1:59:03.611
Stefano?

1:59:09.359 --> 1:59:11.359
I love him.

1:59:12.800 --> 1:59:17.645
I can't see any other explanation
for being in this state.

1:59:18.116 --> 1:59:20.836
That's the only thing it can be.

1:59:21.650 --> 1:59:23.650
I love him.

1:59:25.496 --> 1:59:27.496
I know I'm crazy.

1:59:29.444 --> 1:59:32.684
Every morning when I wake up,
I open my eyes and I see your face...

1:59:32.784 --> 1:59:34.784
...and I start crying.

1:59:37.612 --> 1:59:41.777
I realize that with you,
my life is passing me by.

1:59:45.449 --> 1:59:48.498
How can you stay so calm?

1:59:48.498 --> 1:59:51.210
How can you bear that?

1:59:51.211 --> 1:59:52.992
