might enter its phase of contraction.

2:03:38.798 --> 2:03:40.798
The Big Crunch.

2:03:44.295 --> 2:03:46.675
So what will become of time?

2:03:49.750 --> 2:03:51.750
Will it reverse?

2:03:58.049 --> 2:04:00.089
No one knows the answer.

2:04:05.080 --> 2:04:05.981
Where is Peter?

