2:04:14.073 --> 2:04:15.599
But...

2:04:15.699 --> 2:04:18.023
Drop it. In live you get one take.

2:04:18.123 --> 2:04:21.098
If it's bad, you just deal with it.

2:04:49.610 --> 2:04:51.610
You know him?

2:04:52.110 --> 2:04:54.148
We work together.

2:04:55.656 --> 2:04:59.131
