2:05:33.558 --> 2:05:35.830
My sincerest condolences.

2:05:35.986 --> 2:05:37.986
Peter was a colleague.

2:05:38.338 --> 2:05:39.322
Of course.

2:05:39.422 --> 2:05:42.907
I've seen your show.
Thank you for coming.

2:06:15.596 --> 2:06:17.595
