to your sleep suits.

2:06:51.966 --> 2:06:55.269
You will also receive your...

2:06:55.747 --> 2:06:57.539
Hi.

2:06:57.639 --> 2:06:59.639
I'm Nemo.

2:06:59.754 --> 2:07:01.448
Anna...

2:07:01.548 --> 2:07:03.548
Nice to meet you.

2:07:07.551 --> 2:07:09.591
What brings you to Mars?

2:07:09.828 --> 2:07:14.801
I'm measuring the distance between
Mars and Earth at it's greatest.

2:07:14.901 --> 2:07:17.121
I study time. You know...

2:07:17.675 --> 2:07:22.860
Thing that makes it so that
everything doesn't happen at once.

2:07:24.734 --> 2:07:25.559
And?

2:07:25.659 --> 2:07:28.130
The Big Crunch will happen in 2092...

2:07:28.230 --> 2:07:33.415
...and people who can't hang
on that long will get a free run.

2:07:34.240 --> 2:07:35.647
And you?

2:07:35.747 --> 2:07:38.467
I'm just keeping an old promise.

2:07:43.626 --> 2:07:45.295
Hi.

2:07:45.395 --> 2:07:47.395
Hi.

2:07:47.889 --> 2:07:51.204
We ah... met at your husband's funeral.

2:07:51.572 --> 2:07:53.092
Right.

2:07:53.192 --> 2:07:56.976
I had the strangest feeling when
I saw you that we have met before.

2:07:57.076 --> 2:07:59.227
It's called de javu.

2:07:59.228 --> 2:08:01.228
That's not it.

2:08:01.641 --> 2:08:03.293
It's as if...

2:08:03.393 --> 2:08:05.688
...all of this was in real.

2:08:07.435 --> 2:08:11.685
I'm sorry you must think
that I'm completely crazy.

2:08:12.384 --> 2:08:14.885
I'm not trying to flirt with you.

2:08:14.985 --> 2:08:16.509
I am widower myself.

2:08:16.609 --> 2:08:18.909
I... I'm sorry. I have to go.

2:08:19.009 --> 2:08:21.009
May be some other time.

2:08:26.259 --> 2:08:28.259
Nemo?

2:08:28.603 --> 2:08:31.464
