Are you alright?

2:10:31.249 --> 2:10:34.135
When I say three,
you'll be awake.

2:10:35.235 --> 2:10:37.235
One...

2:10:41.360 --> 2:10:43.360
Two...

2:10:48.579 --> 2:10:50.579
Three.

