What do you see?

2:12:12.987 --> 2:12:15.136
He askes me what I see.

2:12:19.468 --> 2:12:21.779
I say, it's an ink stain.

2:12:22.711 --> 2:12:23.599
He says:

2:12:23.699 --> 2:12:25.867
You have to say more.

2:12:26.037 --> 2:12:29.862
I say, it's an ink stain on a sheet of paper.

2:12:30.550 --> 2:12:32.414
No.

2:12:32.514 --> 2:12:36.305
You have to say, what
goes through your mind.

2:12:40.837 --> 2:12:43.035
It makes me think of an inkwell.

2:12:43.135 --> 2:12:45.688
So he says: 'O'key...

2:12:46.767 --> 2:12:48.767
That's fine'.

