You have until tomorrow to vote.

2:13:05.891 --> 2:13:06.792
Vote.

2:13:06.892 --> 2:13:08.846
And win a vacation on the Moon.

2:13:08.946 --> 2:13:10.946
For the whole family.

2:13:11.168 --> 2:13:13.168
Win a trip to the Moon.

2:13:13.580 --> 2:13:17.065
Take a swing at a fabulous golf vacation.

2:13:29.398 --> 2:13:33.223
Have they announced
the results of the voting?

2:13:33.357 --> 2:13:34.675
I'm sorry.

2:13:34.775 --> 2:13:37.492
At my age.

2:13:37.493 --> 2:13:41.280
The candles cost more than a cake.

2:13:45.387 --> 2:13:47.838
I'm not afraid of dying.

2:13:48.142 --> 2:13:51.457
I'm afraid I have'nt been alive enough.

2:13:54.603 --> 2:13:58.938
It should be written on every
schoolroom blackboard.

2:14:00.632 --> 2:14:03.375
Life is a playground.

2:14:04.942 --> 2:14:06.942
Or nothing.

