2:15:28.159 --> 2:15:30.159
Who is this?

2:15:30.434 --> 2:15:32.303
I was told to call this number.

2:15:32.403 --> 2:15:34.403
My name is Nemo Nobody.

2:15:36.167 --> 2:15:38.184
Is this some kind of a joke?

2:15:38.284 --> 2:15:40.284
No. No, I...

2:15:44.974 --> 2:15:46.236
Operator?
